---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 284
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method=Initiation and Spiritual
    Filiation
By: Chang Po-tuan
---
For repairing a broken piece of bamboo ware, you must use bamboo. When
you want your hen to hatch chickens, eggs and not stones must
be-supplied.  Working on medicines of unlike kinds is merely a waste
of energy. What can be better than the true lead for fulfilling the
secrets of the sages?
